default3.7.
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultPublic understanding could be improved by presenting the public with consistent and accurate messages about what climate change is. Corner et al 
default(
default2012
default)
default found that attitudes towards climate change became significantly more sceptical after reading newspaper editorials that made opposing claims about the reality and seriousness of climate change. 
default3.7.1.
default 
defaultA key iss
defaultue here is the media presenting
default 
defaultrepresentative coverage
default on climate change issues 
default(informed by scientific consensus) 
defaultrather than 
defaultgiving equal weighting to 
